<style>
	a {
   		@apply hover:underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 visited:text-purple-800
	}
</style>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
	<header class="text-center mb-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-2">
			Janis Stockhouse Memorial Concert
		</h1>
	</header>
	<main class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
		<div class="prose max-w-none">
			<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-8">
				We are deeply saddened to announce the death of Janis Stockhouse
				on December 23, 2024. She was a beloved member of our community
				and will be greatly missed.
			</p>

			<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
				Please watch this site for more information about a memorial
				concert to celebrate her life and legacy. We will be posting
				information about plans as they come together and ways you can
				help out.
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>

	<aside class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-4">Updates</h2>
		<div class="space-y-4">
			<div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
				<dl>
					<dt class="font-bold">December 30, 2024</dt>
					<dd>
						WFIU Jazz DJ David Brent Johnson will host a tribute to Janis Stockhouse on
						<a href="https://indianapublicmedia.org/justyouandme/">Just You and Me</a>
						from 3:00-5:00 pm EST. It will include Professors Lissa May, Rachel Caswell, and Natalie Boeyink speaking about Ms. Stockhouse.
						See 
						<a href="https://indianapublicmedia.org/about/wfiu-faq.php">here</a> for all the options for listening
						to the program today.
					</dd>
					<dt class="font-bold mt-3">January 19, 2025</dt>
					<dd>
						<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1CvxjJeSQm/">
							Music & Memories: A Tribute to Janis Stockhouse
						</a>
					</dd>
				</dl>
			</div>
		</div>
	</aside>
	<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-200 mb-8">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-4 text-center">
			Contact the Memorial Committee
		</h2>
		<div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
			<i data-lucide="mail" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600"></i>
			<a
				href="mailto:info@stockhouseconcert.org"
				class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
			>
				info@stockhouseconcert.org
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
